### Description

Hello, I wrote a decorator that dynamically injects services using this decorator. But unfortunately, it works strangely for tests.

https://github.com/Angular-RU/autowired

```ts
@Component({
  selector: 'app-root',
  templateUrl: './app.component.html',
  styleUrls: ['./app.component.css']
})
